text: Betty Jane "Kathleen" Crowley (December 26, 1929 - April 23, 2017) was an American actress. She was born in Green Bank, New Jersey. She starred in a number of TV shows and movies throughout the 1950s and 1960s, ending her career in 1970. She was known for her multiple small roles in the TV series Maverick. Crowley died on April 23, 2017 at her home in Green Bank, New Jersey, aged 87. "Obituary for Kathleen Crowley", Wimberg Funeral Home, April 25, 2017.
